  "paragraphs": [
    "Full Color Changes & Custom Graphics",
    "Google Rating",
    "Based on 106 Reviews",
    "Yelp Rating",
    "Based on 2 Reviews",
    "Facebook Rating",
    "Based on 170 Reviews",
    "Full color changes, custom graphics, and stylish accents — professionally installed for a flawless finish. Looking to give your car a fresh new look? Whether you’re after a full color change, custom graphics, or subtle accents, our premium vinyl wrap services provide the ultimate makeover — without the cost of a new paint job. At Front Range Detail Studio, we use top-of-the-line materials and expert installation techniques to transform your vehicle’s appearance while also offering an extra layer of paint protection.",
    "Wide range of colors, textures, and finishes",
    "Vinyl wraps offer endless possibilities for customization while protecting your original paint.",
    "Quick Turnaround: Most full wraps are completed in 3-5 days, depending on complexity.",
    "Full Customization: Choose from a wide range of colors, textures, and finishes — from matte and gloss to metallic and satin.",
    "Non-Permanent: Easily removable without damaging your original paint, perfect for leased vehicles or style changes.",
    "Paint Protection: Acts as a barrier against minor scratches, sun damage, and road debris.",
    "Cost-Effective Alternative to Paint: Get a fresh look at a fraction of the cost of a custom paint job.",
    "Transform the entire look of your car",
    "1. Full Vehicle Color ChangeTransform the entire look of your car with a full-color wrap.",
    "2. Partial Wraps & GraphicsAdd a custom touch without wrapping the entire vehicle.",
    "3. Commercial & Fleet WrapsTurn your vehicle into a moving billboard.",
    "4. Accent Wraps & DetailsSubtle touches for a more unique style.",
    "Preserve the pristine condition of your vehicle with our high-quality Paint Protection Film, or Clear Bra. Our warranty backed PPF acts as an invisible shield, guarding your car’s paint against scratches, stone chips, and road debris. With self-healing technology and a ceramic coating layer applied over the film, our PPF service is the clear choice to protect your investment in South Denver, Colorado",
    "Our clients have one thing in common: they love their vehicle. From the Class A motorhome to the two-door convertible, our team of detail specialists are equipped and experienced to handle all detailing needs anywhere in Metro Denver.",
    "Over 15 years experience in the automotive detailing industry. Car, Trucks, Semi Trucks, SUVs, RVs, Boats & Watercraft.",
    "Our clients have one thing in common: they love their vehicle. From the Class A motorhome to the two-door convertible, our team of detail specialists are equipped and experienced to handle all detailing needs anywhere in Metro Denver.",
